<section xmlns:ns1="http://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codified" xmlns:ns0="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <num>42-501</num>
  <heading>Recognized estates.</heading>
  <text>Estates in land in the District shall be estates of inheritance, estates for life, estates for years, estates at will, and estates by sufferance.</text>
